Peacemaker of Brevoy
	KEY:PFS Scenario 9-03 ~ Peacemaker of Brevoy
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:Chronicle_S09-03.PFSBoon
	VISIBLE:YES
	COST:0
	DESC:Your diplomacy and hard work have made you famous, and the Pathfinders are welcomed guests in Brevoy. All your characters have access to the trait Noble Born from the Kingmaker Player's Guide, treating it as a regional trait rather than a campaign trait. In addition, you may purchase the Country Estate vanity for 10 PP in the nation of Brevoy. This vanity originally appeared in Pathfinder Campaign Setting: Pathfinder Society Field Guide.

